---
title: Salami Spinach Risotto Includes recyclable aluminum tray
description: Imagine rich, creamy risotto made easy in the oven! You'll combine arborio rice and salty bites of salami right in our oven-ready tray (no pans to clean!). When it comes out of the oven, stir in spinach, tangy sun-dried tomato paste, and a swirl of butter for all the feels! Finish with a sprinkle of Parm, chili flakes, and lemon.
